Ludmilla Azova	soprano

voice type	April Evans is an American soprano who has sung with the Opera Orchestra of New York where she sang Irene in Wagner's Rienzi in 1983 and with the Teater Kiel in Germany where she was the soprano soloist in Beethoven's Missa solemnis (1986) and Rainer Kunad's Thomas-Evangelium (1987).	April Evans	soprano
